{"tid":1522114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"現場冇散水wo，冷氣軍師係咪要同現場義士割蓆：冇be water啦，戀戰啦，送頭啦，中計啦？","createTime":"2019-08-31T12:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T14:28:42.000Z","uid":33307,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9854d3b7d7a3f71fb7458b4ec2b4019b8767d796","tid":1522114,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:14:36.000Z","msg":"係咪咁？"},{"pid":"c0f89a347e5b9c00f1280fb8e008ba31f81f1fcc","tid":1522114,"uid":139282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:15:25.000Z","msg":"求吓大家幫手copy呢段去spread開啊<br />\n<br />\n［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#216<br />\n應該冇加料 UV燈照過安全，番簡水、梳打水可行</span><br />\n<br />\n#252<br />\n綠藻濃縮液+薑，開水沖，唔傷皮膚"},{"pid":"83e0bb9fdc19f58b5d84b4ad2432f35a7dbf7a4e","tid":1522114,"uid":196450,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:15:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係啦你最叻啦 講啲有建設性既說話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d167c9b2fe61c88922aae43d7f2c01be4bcc65a9","tid":1522114,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:25:14.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"1b8445267e2924425b0562e9f86e4ced8e5711a5","tid":1522114,"uid":270326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:27:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">BNO平權聯署要人呀！！仲差二萬四千幾人！多你一個係好多！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論續領左未都簽得。<br />\n<br />\nPostcode寫00000或者852<br />\n地區揀香港<br />\n<br />\n聯署網址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=07n8ytxkS9OF8NraT9rIu1tf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=740ff1b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n做完立即廣傳轉發比朋友，係要一傳十，十傳百，快、快、快!<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a162adc7e9f9d53d0866fe067a6207ae2fb3615c","tid":1522114,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:29:15.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"ee7e17ea134ba54cdafcb57f2b1cf805bdbdfcd3","tid":1522114,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:32:40.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"17d2aee35fdde76686270276ab3876738ebe49b2","tid":1522114,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"7830b17096f1123690193479ca72b2da3049eb3e","tid":1522114,"uid":2883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTi